<p>
<h4 style="text-decoration:underline">Shipping Options</h4>

By default all order are normally shipped by First Class Standard post to UK Mainland and Royal Mail Airmail to locations outside the UK.
iFaru.com offer shipping insurance and guarantees as provided by <a href="www.royalmail.com" target="_blank">Royal Mail</a>. This is available at an additional cost. For more information please write to us at <a HREF="mailto:contact@ifaru.com">contact@ifaru.com</a><br> <br>
<br>
</p>

<p>
<h4 style="text-decoration:underline">Shipping Discounts</h4>
iFaru.com applies a 50% discount to the postage and packing cost of each additional item. This is calculated as follows:
  <ul>
    <li>(a) The full shipping price for the item with the highest shipping price in the shopping cart will be applied.</li>
    <li>(b) Every additional item in the cart will be charged as 50% of its full shipping price.</li>
    <li>The final total of the shipping cost is the sum of (a) and (b).
  </ul>
<br>
</p>

